subsection.def:
use (使用), in relation to a
        vaccine, includes distribute, supply, offer for supply, possess, prescribe, dispense and
        administer;

Government contract (政府合約) means a contract to which the Government is a
                party;
                    (L.N. 176 of 2022)

paragraph.content:
by using the eHealth System (Subsidies) or another electronic system
                    specified by the Director in place of the eHealth System (Subsidies);
                    and

a committee established by the Department of Health
                        (Department) and known as the Expert Committee on Clinical
                    Events Assessment Following COVID-19 Immunisation;
